What's happening to us?

39:40.754 --> 39:42.369
l have no idea.

39:44.424 --> 39:49.509
| used to understand
everything, but
nothing makes sense.

39:52.015 --> 39:53.596
We're just human.

39:57.646 --> 39:59.432
You okay with that?

39:59.523 --> 40:03.107
It's actually a relief.

40:03.610 --> 40:07.979
I felt the hunger,
the need to have
power was so numbing.

40:08.782 --> 40:11.239
My mind felt like
it was full of
cotton and ice

40:11.326 --> 40:16.241
and I haven't felt
like this since
I first met you.

40:17.332 --> 40:18.788
(SIGHS)

40:18.875 --> 40:21.912
I pushed you to
become that monster.
It's my fault.

40:22.004 --> 40:23.369
No.

40:24.381 --> 40:26.622
You were just
following orders.
A Company girl.

40:26.717 --> 40:28.173
Exactly. We're both so...

40:28.260 --> 40:29.500
What, powerless?

40:31.638 --> 40:34.220
We can't take
what we want anymore.

40:36.018 --> 40:37.178
Says who?

40:40.689 --> 40:41.974
(MOANS)
